          "name": "Battlecry!",
          "page": 195,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "A surprise raid by a swarm of the insectile zecui can easily wipe out an entire village overnight. When they don't devour their victims immediately, zecuis typically implant them with their own larvae and bury them in sprawling mass graves, where the developing zecui horde can lie dormant for years before suddenly erupting to the surface to wreak havoc on nearby settlements.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
